import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import Grid from '../lib/grid';
import GridCell from '../lib/grid-cell';
import Section from '../lib/section';

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"grid"}}>{`Grid`}</MDXTag>

<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Based on a 12 column grid system.
Adding `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`six`}</MDXTag>{` will give a 50% width, because 6/12 = 50%.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example"}}>{`Example`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={0} __code={'<Grid all>\n  <GridCell six>\n    <Section>Cell 1</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell six>\n    <Section>Cell 2</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell four>\n    <Section>Cell 3</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell four>\n    <Section>Cell 4</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell four>\n    <Section>Cell 5</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n\n  <GridCell three>\n    <Section>Cell 6</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell three>\n    <Section>Cell 7</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell three>\n    <Section>Cell 8</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n  <GridCell three>\n    <Section>Cell 9</Section>\n  </GridCell>\n</Grid>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Grid,GridCell,Section}}>
    <Grid
        all
    >
        <GridCell
            six
        >
            <Section>Cell 1</Section>
        </GridCell>
        <GridCell
            six
        >
            <Section>Cell 2</Section>
        </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        four
    >
        <Section>Cell 3</Section>
    </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        four
    >
        <Section>Cell 4</Section>
    </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        four
    >
        <Section>Cell 5</Section>
    </GridCell>

    <GridCell
        three
    >
        <Section>Cell 6</Section>
    </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        three
    >
        <Section>Cell 7</Section>
    </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        three
    >
        <Section>Cell 8</Section>
    </GridCell>
    <GridCell
        three
    >
        <Section>Cell 9</Section>
    </GridCell>
</Grid>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"grid-1"}}>{`Grid`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Grid} />
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"gridcell"}}>{`GridCell`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={GridCell} />
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
